text: Pervomaysky () is a rural locality (a selo) in Sterlibashevsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 716 as of 2010. There are 10 streets. == Geography == It is located 4 km from Sterlibashevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Pervomaysky, Sterlibashevsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
